      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i think my fiddle leaf fig is getting root bound. it's looking a bit cramped in its pot and the leaves are dropping. what kind of soil should i get for it and how do i repot it without killing it?",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "hey i think my fiddle leaf fig is getting root bound. it's looking a bit cramped in its pot and the leaves are dropping. what kind of soil should i get for it and how do i repot it without killing it?",
